<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="thrill-n">thrill <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /θrɪl/    美 /θrɪl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>激动；刺激：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a thrill of joy / horror 
一阵喜悦/恐怖</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>令人激动 / 兴奋的事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Meeting the famous footballer was a great thrill for the children. 
跟这位著名的足球运动员见面对孩子们来说是一件非常激动人心的事。</p></div></div>